<b>ForumTopics.com</b>

<p />
Got something to talk about? This is the place to do it. Check out our list of
forum topics and see if there's something going on that you like. Need a discussion
space of your own? We'll be happy to talk to you about your needs.

<p />
<b>Why ForumTopics.com?</b><br />
There are quite a few places where you can go talk about "stuff". The break room at work,
the local grocery store, a club meeting, even just walking around in your neighborhood.
But what the Internet does is expand the concept of what "your neighborhood" really means.
By going online, you might find a whole group of folks - just like yourself - that have an
avid interest in, well, something, anything, or even nothing.

<p />
We found that to be true ourselves, and set up this web site to provide a common meeting area
for friends we've never met, people we have a common interest with, and even casual browsers
passing by. So come on in and join a conversation!

